    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a dependable driving experience. While there are some minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, such as small stone chips on the hood and light wear on the driver's seat bolster, the interior is clean and free of odors. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in running order. The engine has suffered a major internal failure and will require a complete rebuild or replacement to become roadworthy again. Additionally, the transmission was slipping significantly prior to the engine failure, and there are multiple electrical issues affecting the dashboard and interior lighting. Externally, the body shows significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. This is a project car best suited for parts or a dedicated restoration effort.",
      "price": 3000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
